>V</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"err\">âˆˆ</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n<p>The issue seems to be that, while <code>G_module</code> extended <code>has_scalar</code>, this does not provide a <code>has_scalar</code> instance for Lean's class resolution.</p>",
