lass=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>  <span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"err\">â€¢</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"err\">â€¢</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"err\">â€¢</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"err\">â€¢</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">G</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">group</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">field</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm_group</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">has_scalar</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">stable</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">G_representation</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">W</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">submodule</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">v</span> <span class=\"err\">âˆˆ</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"err\">â€¢</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">v</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"err\">âˆˆ</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n<p>(I don't understand the finer details of when to extend a class or not.)</p>",
